                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030706-24-defend110 t18030706-24-punish138"></join>
               Confined six months in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>

               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
